title: EkoPlaza
description: Largest nature food store in Delft. Has a small juice bar inside which also serves sandwiches and small meals, a few options are or can be made vegan. The bar closes one hour before the store closes, except on Friday when it stays open till 8pm and on Saturday it starts half an hour later. The kitchen is open till 4:30pm and on Friday till 7pm. The takeaway has the same opening hours as the store. The phone number of the bar is +31-15-2148346. Previously called Van Nature.
